{"tid":2299250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呂智恆被濫捕+濫告事件，大家可以睇返當日負責濫捕果隻中年黑警點樣濫用權力，點樣浪費納稅人金錢","createTime":"2020-11-24T15:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T16:48:38.000Z","uid":230104,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"627154b1c681294abf108b012fe637bb7e6eb3b1","tid":2299250,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201124/FFB32NT2HZHCTL5AZXDUGFQOPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201124%2FFFB32NT2HZHCTL5AZXDUGFQOPY%2F&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=6e5372ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201124%2FFFB32NT2HZHCTL5AZXDUGFQOPY%2F&h=ecc42d6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201124/FFB32NT2HZHCTL5AZXDUGFQOPY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tqHRrr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tqHRrr.png&h=23be9ef7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5fiFC6s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5fiFC6s.png&h=283f8521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裁判官陳炳宙裁決時指，直至控方庭上播放當日案發的影片，法庭才知悉涉案食環署一級督察麥慶安當時沒有穿着制服。麥在盤問下承認當時沒有向被告表明身份，也沒有展示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳官嚴詞批評，控方早已獲取相關片段，卻依賴一個故意隱瞞公職身份的證人，刻意讓被告「墜入圈套」，做法有違公義，「依賴啲咁唔光彩嘅證據去定罪，會令司法制度蒙上污點」。陳官並強調，辯方其實有權申請永久終止聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控方濫用司法程序 被告可取得訟費<br />\n<br />\n辯方申請訟費，批評控方明知客觀事實，仍選擇不合理地檢控。控方反對，指呂不願離場，是自招嫌疑。<br />\n<br />\n陳官再次批評控方濫用司法程序，「片段早已顯示證據上的種種不合理」，故批准辯方訟費申請。"},{"pid":"9611840e861c841dacbed0094a93297be50989ae","tid":2299250,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T15:40:04.000Z","msg":"「我而家就拘捕你」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好威威呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63db80456f9ca426bb0a861a2711e736e5df51f6","tid":2299250,"uid":217683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T15:45:07.000Z","msg":"推 恆仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3208ff4d62dffa8a60c983f4ee06e37b541df200","tid":2299250,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"港共曱甴集團"},{"pid":"303709250d4193c8835bbe2c22cffa239b4ff4f6","tid":2299250,"uid":267548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:08:35.000Z","msg":"認住隻狗先"},{"pid":"0eac9a50ecc4b9c2c50d23dd48e8cb48c3543777","tid":2299250,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:19:09.000Z","msg":"個警察唔知睇返自己原來比人fake左有咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241f39bea0962d304098f3b79006c25583bb7ab4","tid":2299250,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:28:06.000Z","msg":"玩你一身已經贏咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c89aa02b1da3a10ea8dcb67ee01aaa8dccf1c3f","tid":2299250,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0eac9a50ecc4b9c2c50d23dd48e8cb48c3543777","tid":2299250,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:19:09.000Z","msg":"個警察唔知睇返自己原來比人fake左有咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:33:44.000Z","msg":"fake咩？明明D片黑警、律政檢控一早睇晒都堅持告、而唔係告食環俾假口供、證明係想乘機入你罪"},{"pid":"0e6b7cf5a403079fbff68d6c82f89660ae66a295","tid":2299250,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:40:24.000Z","msg":"麥<del><span class=\"x-small\"><span class=\"violet\">慶安</span></span></del>先生有&lt;怯&gt;意~!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪唔夠愛港共政府?! 係咪唔愛黨?!<br